          "key": "cpib6",
          "text": "Google's Gemma 4 family of open models is now available through the Gemini API and Google AI Studio. Built from the same research behind Gemini 3, these models bring advanced reasoning, native function calling, multimodal understanding, and 256K context windows to an open, Apache 2.0-licensed package you can run anywhere.",
